RawQuestion: what is atlanta ga famous for?
ProcessedQuestion: what is atlanta ga famous for

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.013yq)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.013yq ns:olympics.olympic_host_city.olympics_hosted ?x .
}
